title: BRIEF-Dropbox Sees Initial Public Offering Price Per Share To Be Between $18.00 And $20.00
text: March 21, 2018 / 11:01 AM / in 16 minutes BRIEF-Dropbox Sees Initial Public Offering Price Per Share To Be Between $18.00 And $20.00 Reuters Staff 1 Min Read March 21 (Reuters) - Dropbox Inc: * DROPBOX SAYS CURRENTLY ESTIMATED THAT THE INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING PRICE PER SHARE WILL BE BETWEEN $18.00 AND $20.00 - SEC FILING * DROPBOX SAYS IT HAD PREVIOUSLY EXPECTED IPO PRICE PER SHARE BETWEEN $16.00 AND $18.00 PER SHARE Source text: ( bit.ly/2FRbELx ) Further company coverage:
